<plot>Documentary feature about the traditional Viennese cinema "Bellaria", which is specialized in German cinema from the 20s, 30s and 40s and its regular customers, whose idols are stars like Zarah Leander or Karl Schönböck. They're visiting regularly, some of them even daily, to see the movies of their youth.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?064594</url></doc>
